These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
Color: lilac, aquamarine, brown, turquise
Flower: balloon-flower, daffodil, azalea, poppy
1. Color:turquise is on the left of Color:lilac##1
2. Color:lilac is on the right of Color:turquise##1
3. Flower:daffodil is on the far left or far right##3
4. Color:brown is on the right of Flower:azalea##1
5. Flower:poppy is between Flower:daffodil and Flower:azalea##2
6. Color:turquise == Flower:balloon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Color   | turquise | lilac     | brown | aquamarine |
| Flower     | balloon-flower     | azalea | poppy  | daffodil      |

