2. Beverage:water is on the far left or far right##3
3. Food:apricot is on the left of Beverage:water##1
4. Beverage:water is on the right of Beverage:coffee##1
5. Food:grapefruit is on the far right##1
6. Beverage:tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Food   | pomegranate | kiwi    | apricot     | grapefruit  |
| Beverage     | tea    | lemonade | coffee | water |

